            <font size=3D"3" face=3D"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>
            <b>FAO: A special online forum in English that will explore
some of=20
            the challenges that people and projects face when
implementing projects=20
            aimed at empowering women and ICTs in rural livelihoods<br>
            </b>5 - 16 July<br>
            The forum &quot;Gender, ICTs and Rural Livelihoods&quot; will
look=20
            at what has worked, what has not worked, and good practices,
as well=20
            as the critical area of capacity building and what can be
done to=20
            empower women and men in playing a more vital role in ICTs
for agriculture=20
            and rural development. <br>
            <br>
            Furthermore, the Forum aims to explore evaluation and will
facilitate=20
            discussion on how we produce evidence that donors need to
take the=20
            importance of women in rural ICTs seriously. <br>
            The forum will be hosted entirely online through the
e-Agriculture=20
            Community<br>
            platform at
<a href=3D"http://www.e-agriculture.org/">http://www.e-agriculture.org</a><=
br>
            <br>
            Simply go to the platform, log in and join the discussions!
