            <br>
            <b>Launch of the LaProf Web Portal<br>
            </b>The LaProf Web Portal
(<a href=3D"http://www.language-learning-portal.eu/">http://www.language-le=
arning-portal.eu</a>)=20
            was publicly launched at the beginning of the month. The
Portal focuses=20
            on the language learning needs of agricultural professionals,
providing=20
            access to digital content on topics such as food management,
horticulture,=20
            animal science, biotechnology, management and many others.
The learning=20
            scenarios aim at supporting the agricultural professionals
throughout=20
            their learning, working and mobility processes. <br>
            <br>
            The LaProf Web portal may be used to find:<br>
            <br>
            * Interactive multilingual language learning units, exercises
and=20
            terminology customized for the agricultural sector<br>
            <br>
            * Multilingual WebQuests with focus on linguistic and
cultural issues=20
            to support immigration processes<br>
            <br>
            * Greek and Finnish language learning resources for beginners
<br>
            <br>
            * Lists of relevant language learning institutions in Greece
and Finland=20
            and other useful information<br>
            <br>
            The multilingual LaProf Portal is currently available in
seven languages=20
            (English, Greek, Romanian, Hungarian, Finnish, Estonian and
Polish)=20
            and next steps envisage its development in Russian and French
language.=20
            It has been developed in the context of the LaProf project
(www.laprof.eu),=20
            a multilateral project that is funded by the Lifelong
Learning Programme=20
            of the European Commission.<br>
            <br>
            We cordially invite you to visit the LaProf Web Portal and
find resources=20
            of interest/relevance to your work at: <a
href=3D"http://www.language-learning-portal.eu/">www.language-learning-port=
al.eu</a><br>
            <br>
            We also kindly ask you to take 5 minutes of your time to let
us know=20
            how it looked at:
<a href=3D"http://survey.agroknow.gr/index.php?sid=3D67922&amp;lang=3Den">h=
ttp://survey.agroknow.gr/index.php?sid=3D67922&amp;lang=3Den</a><br>
            <br>
            See:
<a href=3D"http://www.language-learning-portal.eu/">http://www.language-lea=
rning-portal.eu</a><br>
            <br>
            Contact: Jan PAWLOWSKI, Marjo HALMIALA<br>
            E-mail: jan.pawlowski(at)titu.jyu.fi,
marjo.halmiala(at)jyu.fi<br>
